Maintainer: Nicolas Frerebeau
    <nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr>
Description: An implementation of Paul Tol's colour schemes,
    ready for each type of data, with colours that are distinct for all
    people, including colour-blind readers. This package also provides
    several thematic palettes (geologic timescale, land cover, FAO soils,
    etc.) with scales for 'ggplot2'.
License: GPL-3
URL: http://khroma.archaeo.science,
